Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 22:00:01 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 20/21] feat(analytics): add per-model TTFT, Token/s and error
 metrics in Model Usage table

- Add get_performance_metrics_by_model() DB method
- Extend ModelAnalyticsEntry with avg_ttft_ms, avg_tokens_per_second, error_rate
- Update /analytics/models endpoint to populate per-model performance
- Add TTFT, Token/s, Errors columns to Model Usage table with sort support
---
